        "Description": "Good evening, 47.\r\rYour targets are three operatives embedded within Chongqing’s criminal tech sector. Internally, they are known as The Spectrum, and can be easily recognised by their coloured attire, with each operative dressed in a single, identifiable colour.\r\rThe client requires the group dismantled. Eliminate all three targets and ensure their organisation cannot recover.",
